Since I have been tagged by @lavinaheryawan @christycty and @irenaputrika , guess I'll just have to do it.. So here are 20 facts about me!
1. Je m'apelle Hana Noviana Sanjaya. 
2. I came to this world on 29th afternoon of November, 1995.
3. I was named after a lotus that bloomed in the hospital the day when I was born. So that is why my name is Hana, derived from Japanese word of flower.
4. I love languages and I wish to be a polyglot.
5. Such an avid reader. Would choose buying new books to new clothes. Yes, I'm bookworm just like that.
6. I love my piggy doll so much!
7. Proud Akunpar '14
8. My dream jobs (yes with that s) include being a cinemmatographer/director, want to work for the UN, well, the list goes on..
9. Love almost any genres of music except heavy metal and black metal.
10. Some are suprised when they know that I love EDM.
11. I love the smell of roses.
12. Do a lot of embarassing dances at home together with @inaxiao and @lukmancs
13. Dibilang mirip banget sama koko gw.. Ada teller bilang kita kayak kembar üòí
14. I have love/hate relationship with kpop and kdrama.. But  mostly would say no to that.
15. Invented "BIG FAT AMEN TO THAT" ahahaha ceritanya buat suntikan motivasi
16. Suka tiba2 bikin phrase ato noises kalo lagi ngobrol sama orang. Well, ceritanya biar ekspresif...
17. I love talking in accents, still can't nail Scottish and French and Gangsta accent, though.
18. Punya account instagram gara2 #instagramlyricvideo nya Fedde Le Grand
19. I curse a lot #sorrynotsorry hahhahah harus ngurangin tapinya! 
20. Mulai kehabisan ide. Aaaaand ketika nanti pas udh dipost pasti ada kepikir mau tulis apa dan gw lgsg fase rage. That happens a lot.

For those of you who have been tagged, well, you know what to do.. #20facts about me!
